00:57.285 --> 00:58.880
Will that be all, sir?

01:00.630 --> 01:02.624
As a matter of fact, there's

01:02.624 --> 01:05.129
something I wanna talk to you about.

01:10.805 --> 01:13.030
I received another
one of your letters.

01:13.030 --> 01:15.850
Don't try to deny that it was you.

01:15.850 --> 01:17.921
Before I made the last drop,

01:17.921 --> 01:20.369
I marked the bills.

01:20.369 --> 01:23.911
Then I found them in your room.

01:23.911 --> 01:26.665
Since when is blackmail
on your list of duties?

01:26.665 --> 01:29.511
Master Paul, I don't know
what to say.

01:29.511 --> 01:31.297
I wasn't thinking straight.

01:31.297 --> 01:32.863
You weren't thinking straight?

01:32.863 --> 01:37.256
No, sir. The grief. Your father's death
and your step-mother.

01:37.256 --> 01:39.414
It won't happen again.

